    "body": "Instead of putting the whole `validator_definitions.yml` on the secure storeage and symlinking, you could replace  `voting_keystore_password: <password>` in `validator_definitions.yml`  with `voting_keystore_password_path: /secure_storage/password.txt` The VC should fail to start up if it has no access to `/secure_storage/password.txt`",
